Conclusion
DFS (O(2^n), O(n!)) (思想:构建搜索树+判断可行性)
1. Find all possible solutions
2. Permutations / Subsets
BFS (O(m), O(n))
1. Graph traversal (每个点只遍历一次)
2. Find shortest path in a simple graph